{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC07_LEO_210.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x1e,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Leoooon!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Ah, Sophie. You seem like you're in a good mood."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe. I actually have a present for you! Tadah!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Is this... A brooch? Did you make this?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yeah, I worked really hard to make it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "I see... So this is for me... Hehe, I'm really happy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "All the expensive jewelry I've had until now doesn't even compare..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "T-that's an exaggeration. It's not really that expensive at all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "No, having the highest price doesn't always mean something's the most valuable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "The price doesn't matter, I'm sure this brooch will be something I treasure all my life. Thank you, Sophie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x4c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I'm glad you like it so much. You didn't seem very happy lately, after all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "It's true that I felt a little depressed. But... That was solved thanks to you, too."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Huh...? What do you mean?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x43,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "I told you just now... The highest priced item isn't always the most valuable."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x44,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "The brooch you gave me helped me realize that."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "I'm sorry. I still don't follow..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2b,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "I'm saying that my dream wasn't actually to become the top clothier in my country."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2a,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "What!? Really?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I had forgotten about this for a long time, but my real dream was to create clothes that make people smile."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Clothes... That make people smile..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Yup. You two were really happy when you wore the clothes I made, right? That's the kind of stuff I wanted to create."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "It's more important to me to see people smile, not getting top awards at some contest."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "I see... So that's how you felt."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I've been chasing a different dream up until now. No wonder I wasn't satisfied when I reached it."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x1b,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Argh, I feel like an idiot for being so worried about it. But I also feel really relieved."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Ehehe, that's good. You're much cooler when you're happy and confident, though!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x3c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, yeah. Anyway, now that I've realized that, I can't just sit around forever."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x8,
            "name_id": 0x8,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "I'll keep working at it, so feel free to come to my shop anytime."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I got it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x3,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0x26,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "Leon learned the skill \"<CLGR>Likes Cute Things<CLNR>\"."
        }
    ]
}